Author: whyamitoblame
Text: TW: calories When my therapist asked me to go to my GP, and my GP suggested upping calories to at least 1'000 - 1'200 a day and I just couldn't do it. I thought i head it all under control and could change whenever I wanted to. But, that's when i realised i was wrong.

Text: I feel like for me that shit rly hit when I flavored my appetite suppressant with lemon
